videos.description: Frankie Ferrari gets left all alone by Gonzaga defenders and knocks down a tying 3-pointer for the Dons.
videos.headline: Ferrari hits open 3-pointer for San Fran

videos.description: Josh Perkins gets by his defender and finger rolls for the and-1 bucket.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Perkins crosses over for and-1

videos.description: Josh Perkins and Killian Tillie team up for some ping-pong passing to Jonathan Williams who dunks down low.
videos.headline: Quick passing leads to Zags dunk

videos.description: San Francisco's Frankie Ferrari keeps his team in it his a pull-up 3-pointer in the second half.
videos.headline: Ferrari pulls up for Dons 3-pointer

videos.description: Gonzaga's Slias Melson picks up a poor pass and races down court for the slam.
videos.headline: Melson throws down on steal and dunk

videos.description: Rui Hachimura shuts down Souley Boom with a minute to go in regualtion.
videos.headline: Hachimura gets late block for Zags
